messages.content: are you going to fly me to objective?
messages.speaker: Conor Robinson

messages.content: Yes, I will be flying you to the objective. We need to be careful though, the enemy has been known to set up traps along the route. Have you checked your gear to make sure you're all set for the mission, Conor?
messages.speaker: Benjamin Collins

messages.content: Great to hear, Conor. Let's get strapped in and make our way to the objective. Keep your eyes peeled for any potential threats, and if we encounter any trouble, I'll provide cover from above while you do your thing on the ground. Stay sharp and stay safe, my friend.
messages.speaker: Benjamin Collins
